blueprint.label: SpaceX Mall
blueprint.description:
- Will fit within a single block using rail "spurs" off a full-length siding track.  Leave room for a Construction Site.
- The iron-stick assembler at the top-right can be changed to iron pipe to produce boilers.
- Change the refinery recipe to "basic" until "advanced" is researched.  Manually move plastic to (outside) Advanced Circuits assemblers.

alert_parameters.alert_message: Load Is More Than Rocket Can Hold
